{"tid":2393780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"昂山素姬反對西方國家就牠被拘留一事，粗暴干涉緬甸軍方內政","createTime":"2021-02-03T17:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T04:41:55.000Z","uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"713d4b56155ba5110999362d5796cc57d3bd7fd1","tid":2393780,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:10:36.000Z","msg":"訪問緬甸的國家主席習近平今天與國務資政昂山素姬舉行會談，雙方決定共建中緬命運共同體，開啟雙邊關係的新時代。兩國簽署33項合作文件，包括落實耗資13億美元（約100億港元）皎漂深水港等基建項目。「路遙知馬力，患難見真情」，習近平強調，將繼續在國際上為緬方仗義執言，支持緬方維護國家尊嚴和正當權益。因羅興亞危機而受到西方社會指責的昂山素姬說，有的國家以人權、宗教為借口粗暴干涉別國內政，希望中方繼續在國際場合為緬甸等中小國家主持公道。"},{"pid":"6f73c5b85f8809f602736c71598b007fda2c78d4","tid":2393780,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be337a954af5bb05f6901606d391fdd8d7260e39","tid":2393780,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:13:30.000Z","msg":"昂山素雞在獄中反對其他國家說三道四"},{"pid":"c4f69392ebe3c3b3799709dfe90e7611b09c2d98","tid":2393780,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T21:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879432d55312b56b67eb4331b0ad224e23bd0256","tid":2393780,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2cab6f97ada7ce999839df8a533827ba3bb2ba","tid":2393780,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:41:55.000Z","msg":"幾時拍片認罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw 玩撚完假標題未?"}]}